06T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"【2021首個行動post】全民文宣連儂日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=407a952a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&h=2eee38b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=WjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.xx&amp;oh=fb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b&amp;oe=601C7DDA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3DWjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-2.xx%26oh%3Dfb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b%26oe%3D601C7DDA&h=3f6a81b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/136684605_2741317896183001_8531677324604596330_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=d9g0bNygB_0AX8B4SeH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.xx&amp;oh=a27fe705576225eb6df9a42f188ac677&amp;oe=601B6C6D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F136684605_2741317896183001_8531677324604596330_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3Dd9g0bNygB_0AX8B4SeH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-2.xx%26oh%3Da27fe705576225eb6df9a42f188ac677%26oe%3D601B6C6D&h=b64d87f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/136639341_2741317929516331_1099685243406799757_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=ESmQ7mI_jGwAX_ZEkFh&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.xx&amp;oh=356af3cfef1b1500d977554245f89cd5&amp;oe=601A92AB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F136639341_2741317929516331_1099685243406799757_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3DESmQ7mI_jGwAX_ZEkFh%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-1.xx%26oh%3D356af3cfef1b1500d977554245f89cd5%26oe%3D601A92AB&h=bc15e78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明未來到，先有大抓捕。<br />\n抗爭平靜片刻，港共立即反噬。<br />\n港共就係要我地恐懼。<br />\n要我地放棄。<br />\n要我地徒勞。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨抗爭意志不滅。<br />\n8/1-11/1，星光燎原，遍地開花！<br />\n寧鳴而死，不默而生！"},{"pid":"3e4cfe7cf402b1622cbe4d88c15ceb6a3ac033ad","tid":2355731,"uid":324629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"97ad81f6ac3a33af6e6c6da60f71958bf8b11003","tid":2355731,"uid":263261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"on9有冇大台都拉架啦<br />\n你估你而家係香港仲有人敢出去遊行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a3f0b7dd6f449444721bb958620020358ddf77","tid":2355731,"uid":43785,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"79956ada152e00e737c1c547b0cfdfc48c9110fd","tid":2355731,"uid":52939,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"無大台攪下事攪下D有廉恥既政府就得<br />\n對住連細路女都姦得殺得既狗正苦,無組織無統一號令一定收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"依家係所謂既有組織<br />\n同統一號令果個都係鳩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你信唔信李卓人會帶你去抗爭？<br />\n信唔信林卓廷尹兆堅嗰啲人，可以帶領到大家去組織行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信唔信鄺俊宇楊岳橋可以幫你講得贏嗰政府？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話佢地廢，我想講香港市民當初唔應該將個波交畀佢哋之後，只聽佢地號令就算數<img src